reviewText: Its a great little addition to the Jingle and Bell's collection.  I just wish there was more lines where the dogs respond.

We bought this for our 5 & 6 year old (and for us) This should be added to your Christmas video collection that you watch every year.  Heart warming story that we all love.  If you are a dog lover you will especially enjoy it.
Bought this for my 4 year old granddaughter for her to watch over the Christmas period. She loved it and it helped ease for a time the fact that she was not well.
great color,  My grand daughters  loved the story
So excited to see the reaction of our two great-grands when we watch this at our family gathering this Christmas.  Jingles and Bell are two of their favorite toys.
I love Jingle the husky pup!
The movie arrived on Christmas Eve, just in time to be wrapped for my 2 year old nephew. The joy of seeing the surprise & excitement on his little face made the purchase priceless! I was thrilled!
The 3 year old granddaughter loves it. It's better then watching the tv tape I made that has commercials. When it's over she asks to see it again.
Super cute Hallmark movies on dvd. About 22ish minutes each. I think they're stop action. My toddler really likes the dogs and the barking sounds they make. DVD was legit.
